<br>
Now dex is that thing... it determins many secondary things such as (most important) how many times your weapons procs, and how fast you learn weapon skills... Now Barbarians start out with only little (80) dex. This is not enough in my oppinion. since their str is already high, I would suggest putting atleast 15 points into that... and the rest in str. all the other stats can easyly be enhanced with armor.<br>
<br>
This is my personal oppinion since it is a INCREDIBLE pain to get back stab maxed if you have low dex...<br>
<br>
Hope this helps,<br>
<br>
Tinli 46 Rogue<br>
